{"tid":359193,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實外國人係咪真係咁高(原來韓國男人平均得173CM)","createTime":"2017-08-14T10:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T14:12:24.000Z","uid":109077,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d203bac01dc1669421e799fece3140a2ef2045c6","tid":359193,"uid":109077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:02:56.000Z","msg":"我就未去過西方國家<br />\n好好奇鬼佬係唔係真係個個180?<br />\n就咁睇數據，其實好少國家男人平均身高有180以上<br />\n<br />\n就算係所謂亞洲最高既韓國，平均身高其實只係173(19歲)<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Oy6NNju.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOy6NNju.png&h=16517f8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知邊個港女吹到個個180<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁西方國家又點?"},{"pid":"cdfd5773c0775289cfcc8fd4c549968d9a989ac2","tid":359193,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:03:39.000Z","msg":"how about hong kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0d1fb1a72b47981debdd43c75e1d0b63d63fc4","tid":359193,"uid":135707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:05:38.000Z","msg":"亞洲最高平均都得173 咁班港男呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e3b3592b52c187f7a977b2c00170407655c0e7","tid":359193,"uid":19252,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:09:04.000Z","msg":"澳洲d人好高，女個個都175以上，鬼佬真係個個180以上，190都好多"},{"pid":"016a0075af6ec221939933156c8b4adb7ea02233","tid":359193,"uid":70163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:09:36.000Z","msg":"米9 型男表示打和啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208296419a25ad7f258399d99da7c2d74197004d","tid":359193,"uid":99720,"like":2,"dislike":0